<!-- Moved from templates/posts/default.php -->

    <div><p><a title="Companies > Capcom [2,662 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/capcom">Capcom</a> will host a <a href="https://www.capcom-games.com/showcase/spotlight/en-us/" target="_blank">Capcom Spotlight</a> broadcast on <a href="https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?iso=20260305T2200" target="_blank">March 5 at 2:00 p.m. PT / 5:00 p.m. ET / June 27 at 7:00 JST</a>, the company announced. You will be able to watch it on YouTube (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6iIAJOHTnbA" target="_blank">English</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@capcom" target="_blank">Japanese</a>). <span id="more-1030058"></span></p><p>The 30-minute broadcast will feature “the latest information about Capcom’s upcoming releases.” Featured titles include <em><a title="Games > Mega Man: Dual Override [1 article]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mega-man-dual-override">Mega Man: Dual Override</a></em> (the reveal of the Excellence Awards winners for the Robot <a title="Companies > Mas [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/mas">Mas</a>ter Design Contest), <em><a title="Games > Mega Man Star Force Legacy Collection [3 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/mega-man-star-force-legacy-collection">Mega Man Star Force Legacy Collection</a></em> (information on online features), <em><a title="Games > Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/monster-hunter-stories-3-twisted-reflection">Monster Hunter Stories 3: Twisted Reflection</a></em>, <em><a title="Games > PRAGMATA [12 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/pragmata">PRAGMATA</a></em>, and <em><a title="Games > Street Fighter 6 [54 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/street-fighter-6">Street Fighter 6</a></em>.</p><p>Watch a teaser trailer below.</p><h2><span>Teaser Trailer</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="Capcom Spotlight - March 2026" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7W7T3xAgKOI?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
